{"tid":404610,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"好期待港產動作片《MRS K》惠英紅、伍佰、任達華","createTime":"2017-09-18T08:45:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T14:00:34.000Z","uid":129206,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bc5291895742cbd9bcd39e918ba344af952e2e91","tid":404610,"uid":129206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T08:45:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XNeDprEQEvo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXNeDprEQEvo&d=Y8qSumg6seHukszPxWBdZRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=5f02a70b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XNeDprEQEvo</a><br />\n　<br />\n呢部係惠英紅最後一部動作片，因為唔係中國合拍，只有7百幾萬成本，預非常低，但抱住港產片動作片精神下，睇下佢點武戲文拍，文戲武拍先！本土電影動作片究竟可唔可以搞得起呢？係唔係一定去到合拍片《貪狼》同《戰狼》上億先可以拍動作？<br />\n　<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170203/photo/bkn-20170203061501153-0203_00862_001_01p.jpg?20170203131839\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170203%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170203061501153-0203_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20170203131839&h=4e6deefc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://blog.hkmovie6.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/MrsK_1-1024x767.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.hkmovie6.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F12%2FMrsK_1-1024x767.jpg&h=fc3893b3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a046374e31c01443c697ea51ca801026713f6d82","tid":404610,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T09:08:51.000Z","msg":"惠英紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"709dcec0a113c5e585c3c50f327cb482a86f4d97","tid":404610,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T09:19:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"924224c23ce3b14f7c09fb49d2996dbaf5a7d667","tid":404610,"uid":38576,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"repl